--- Hakuna Matata ---
Introducing Hakuna Matata, the cutting-edge solution for intermittent encryption. With intermittent encryption, it is undetectable and can encrypt terabytes of data in just a few minutes
Every time you open this app, a unique public and private key is generated exclusively for you. You don't need to worry about the private and public key. No one can decrypt files that you have encrypted.
